      *----                                                                   00
           EVALUATE EIBAID                                                    00
               WHEN  DFHENTER                                                 00
                     DISPLAY ' APERTEI ENTER'
                     PERFORM 1000-LER-ARQUIVO                                 00
               WHEN  DFHPF4                                                   00
                     DISPLAY ' APERTEI F4'
