                               FLENGTH(LENGTH OF MATRICULA)                   00
           END-EXEC                                                           00
      *----                                                                   00
           EXEC CICS READ     FILE (ARQ-VSAM)                                 00
                              RIDFLD(MATRICULA)                               00
