                             FROM(REGISTRO-VSAM)                              00
                             LENGTH(LENGTH OF REGISTRO-VSAM)                  00
                             RESP(RESP1)                                      00
                             RESP2(RESP2)                                     00
           END-EXEC                                                           00
      *----                                                                   00

           IF RESP1 NOT EQUAL DFHRESP(NORMAL)                                 00
